STATE of North Carolina
v.
Aggrey Winston MANNING No. 121P15-3 Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 11, 2019 Aggrey W. Manning, for Manning, Aggrey W. Amy Kunstling Irene, Special Deputy Attorney General, Roger A. Echols, District Attorney, for State of N.C.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 7th of January 2019 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the North Carolina Court of Appeals, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 11th of June 2019."

Ervin, J. and Davis J. recused
